parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the DRC system can cause the vehicle to become unstable and difficult to control, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle bounces or jumps over bumps
leans excessively during turns
has uneven tire wear
and may have a rattling or banging noise coming from the suspension. In some cases
the vehicle may become difficult to steer or may lose contact with the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Hydraulic Fluid Leaks in DRC System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaks in the DRC system can cause the system to fail, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Hydraulic fluid leaks
uneven tire wear
and a rattling or banging noise coming from the suspension.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Shock Absorber Failure in DRC System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the shock absorbers in the DRC system can cause the vehicle to become unstable and difficult to control, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle bounces or jumps over bumps
leans excessively during turns
and may have uneven tire wear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank rollover valve can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents, posing a significant risk to vehicle occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: Strong smell of fuel or fuel vapor
fuel leaks on the driver's side in front of the rear tire
fuel leaks when filling the tank above 3/4th's
fuel puddles on the ground.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the transmission to slip, leading to loss of power, difficulty accelerating, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the transmission slips
difficulty accelerating
power failure to the wheels
the vehicle is unable to accelerate quickly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause loss of power, difficulty accelerating, and increased risk of accidents, especially when merging into traffic.
symptoms: The transmission slips
difficulty accelerating
power failure to the wheels
the vehicle is unable to accelerate quickly
the transmission needs to be rebuilt.
